snippet.title: European Gaming and Betting Association
snippet.description:
The European Gaming and Betting Association (EGBA) is the Brussels-based trade association representing the leading online gambling operators established, licensed, and regulated within the EU, including bet365, Betsson Group, Entain, Flutter, Kindred Group, and William Hill. EGBA works together with national and EU authorities and other stakeholders towards a well-regulated and well-channelled online gambling market which provides a high level of consumer protection and takes account of the realities of the internet and online consumer demand. EGBA member companies meet the highest regulatory standards and, in 2021, had 225 online gambling licenses to provide their services to 29,8 million customers across 21 different European countries. Currently, EGBA members account for 33% of Europe’s online gambling gross gaming revenue (GGR).

For more information visit: http://www.egba.eu

snippet.title: Jenders Gaming
snippet.description:
Welcome to the channel! 
Here it's all about Board games, card games, miniature games, and wargaming. If it fits on a tabletop I love to play it and try it out! On this channel you will learn about new and older games, I will teach you how to set up the game and how to play it. 

I will show you brand new board games that will launch on Kickstarter but also games that you will find in store.
But it´s not just games, occasionally I paint miniatures and give you a step-by-step on how to paint your own minis. Every now and then I also show some amazing tabletop terrain and game mats,  to level up your gaming experience!  I simply love the world of miniatures, board games, card games, role play and I want to share that love with you! So come join me!  

Videos are released every week so be sure you subscribe to the channel not to miss out.  :)  

#boardgame #tabletop #boardgamereview #tabletopterrain #miniatures #boardgamegeek #tabletopgames #gamer
